Title: Camp Hideout
Written by:
Kat Olson 
 C. Neil Davenport 
 Dave DeBorde
Starring:
Corbin Bleu 
 Ethan Drew 
 Amanda Leighton 
 Christopher Lloyd
Production: Filming occurred in Franklin, Tennessee in October 2021.
Release: In May 2023, it was announced that Roadside Attractions acquired U.S. distribution rights to the film. Camp Hideout was released in theaters on September 15, 2023.
On the review aggregator website Rotten Tomatoes, 40% of five critics' reviews are positive, with an average rating of 4.8/10.
